{"data":[{"date":"07:01 25/07","title":"Kh\u00f4ng du \u0111\u1ea5u c\u00f9ng Juventus, Ronaldo sang Trung Qu\u1ed1c qu\u1ea3ng b\u00e1 th\u01b0\u01a1ng hi\u1ec7u","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/25/6.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i tham gia chuy\u1ebfn du \u0111\u1ea5u h\u00e8 c\u00f9ng Juventus, Cristiano Ronaldo sang Trung Qu\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ec3 qu\u1ea3ng b\u00e1 cho nh\u00e0 t\u00e0i tr\u1ee3 Nike c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 th\u01b0\u01a1ng hi\u1ec7u c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n mang t\u00ean CR7.\r\n\r\n</h2><div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Cristiano Ronaldo sang Trung Qu\u1ed1c qu\u1ea3ng b\u00e1 th\u01b0\u01a1ng hi\u1ec7u h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Cristiano Ronaldo sang Trung Qu\u1ed1c qu\u1ea3ng b\u00e1 th\u01b0\u01a1ng hi\u1ec7u h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/25/Cristiano-Ronaldo-sang-Trung-Quoc-quang-ba-thuong-hieu-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>Kh\u00f4ng du \u0111\u1ea5u c\u00f9ng Juventus do \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ngh\u1ec9 sau k\u1ef3 World Cup 2018, Cristiano Ronaldo sang Trung Qu\u1ed1c qu\u1ea3ng b\u00e1 th\u01b0\u01a1ng hi\u1ec7u.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"width: 100%;\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Ronaldo gay chu y khi luon duoc mot ve si luc luong theo sat nhu hinh voi bong.\" title=\"Ronaldo g\u00e2y ch\u00fa \u00fd khi lu\u00f4n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ed9t v\u1ec7 s\u0129 l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng theo s\u00e1t nh\u01b0 h\u00ecnh v\u1edbi b\u00f3ng.\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/25/2.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>Ronaldo g\u00e2y ch\u00fa \u00fd khi lu\u00f4n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ed9t v\u1ec7 s\u0129 l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng theo s\u00e1t nh\u01b0 h\u00ecnh v\u1edbi b\u00f3ng.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"width: 100%;\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Ronaldo sang Trung Quoc de quang ba cho Nike cung nhu thuong hieu CR7 cua ban than. Nike coi Trung Quoc la thi truong trong diem, trong khi Adidas dat trong tam thi truong o Nhat Ban.\" title=\"Ronaldo sang Trung Qu\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ec3 qu\u1ea3ng b\u00e1 cho Nike c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 th\u01b0\u01a1ng hi\u1ec7u CR7 c\u1ee7a b\u1ea3n th\u00e2n. Nike coi Trung Qu\u1ed1c l\u00e0 th\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1eddng tr\u1ecdng \u0111i\u1ec3m, trong khi Adidas \u0111\u1eb7t tr\u1ecdng t\u00e2m th\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1eddng \u1edf Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n.\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/25/065845-3.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>Ronaldo sang Trung Qu\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ec3 qu\u1ea3ng b\u00e1 cho Nike c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 th\u01b0\u01a1ng hi\u1ec7u CR7 c\u1ee7a b\u1ea3n th\u00e2n. Nike coi Trung Qu\u1ed1c l\u00e0 th\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1eddng tr\u1ecdng \u0111i\u1ec3m, trong khi Adidas \u0111\u1eb7t tr\u1ecdng t\u00e2m th\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1eddng \u1edf Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"width: 100%;\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Ronaldo gop mat o Trung tam The thao Olympic Bac Kinh de day cac cau thu tre mot so ky nang co ban.\" title=\"Ronaldo g\u00f3p m\u1eb7t \u1edf Trung t\u00e2m Th\u1ec3 thao Olympic B\u1eafc Kinh \u0111\u1ec3 d\u1ea1y c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 k\u1ef9 n\u0103ng c\u01a1 b\u1ea3n.\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/25/4.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>Ronaldo g\u00f3p m\u1eb7t \u1edf Trung t\u00e2m Th\u1ec3 thao Olympic B\u1eafc Kinh \u0111\u1ec3 d\u1ea1y c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 k\u1ef9 n\u0103ng c\u01a1 b\u1ea3n.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"width: 100%;\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Cau thu 33 tuoi cung bieu dien ky thuat ca nhan de truyen cam hung cho cac cau thu tre.\" title=\"C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 33 tu\u1ed5i c\u0169ng bi\u1ec3u di\u1ec5n k\u1ef9 thu\u1eadt c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n \u0111\u1ec3 truy\u1ec1n c\u1ea3m h\u1ee9ng cho c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb.\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/25/5.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 33 tu\u1ed5i c\u0169ng bi\u1ec3u di\u1ec5n k\u1ef9 thu\u1eadt c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n \u0111\u1ec3 truy\u1ec1n c\u1ea3m h\u1ee9ng cho c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"width: 100%;\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Chuyen di cua Ronaldo toi Trung Quoc du kien se keo dai 1 tuan.\" title=\"Chuy\u1ebfn \u0111i c\u1ee7a Ronaldo t\u1edbi Trung Qu\u1ed1c d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn s\u1ebd k\u00e9o d\u00e0i 1 tu\u1ea7n.\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/25/6.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>Chuy\u1ebfn \u0111i c\u1ee7a Ronaldo t\u1edbi Trung Qu\u1ed1c d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn s\u1ebd k\u00e9o d\u00e0i 1 tu\u1ea7n.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft kh\u00e1c tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn v\u1ec1 Cristiano Ronaldo h\u00e8 2018:</h2>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-italia/cristiano-ronaldo-vang-mat-trong-chuyen-du-dau-he-cua-juventus-176-191800.html\">Cristiano Ronaldo kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec1n t\u00ean trong danh s\u00e1ch du \u0111\u1ea5u h\u00e8 c\u1ee7a Juventus</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-italia/cristiano-ronaldo-kiem-them-bao-nhieu-tien-cho-juventus-176-191796.html\">Cristiano Ronaldo s\u1ebd ki\u1ebfm th\u00eam kho\u1ea3ng bao nhi\u00eau ti\u1ec1n cho Juventus?</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-italia/neymar-tin-ronaldo-se-toa-sang-tren-dat-y-176-191698.html\">Neymar tin Ronaldo s\u1ebd t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t \u00dd</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/nhan-vat/ronaldo-cap-ben-turin-juve-co-con-la-juve-389-191603.html\">Ronaldo c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Turin:  Juve c\u00f3 c\u00f2n l\u00e0\u2026 Juve?</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/hau-truong/ngoi-sao-ronaldo-bi-in-mat-len-giay-ve-sinh-188-191598.html\">Ng\u00f4i sao Ronaldo b\u1ecb in m\u1eb7t l\u00ean ... gi\u1ea5y v\u1ec7 sinh</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/tin-chuyen-nhuong/ronaldo-ra-di-ai-se-mang-ve-50-ban-thang-moi-mua-cho-real-187-191545.html\">Ronaldo ra \u0111i: Ai s\u1ebd mang v\u1ec1 50 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng m\u1ed7i m\u00f9a cho Real?</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>N.D (TTVN)</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1604","checkdouble":"191950"},{"date":"07:46 25/07","title":"Danh s\u00e1ch c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 hay nh\u1ea5t n\u0103m c\u1ee7a FIFA: Mbappe s\u00e1nh vai c\u00f9ng Ronaldo, Messi","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/25/danh-sach-cau-thu-hay-nhat-nam-cua-fifa-mbappe-sanh-vai-cung-ronaldo-messi.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Leon Bailey r\u1eddi Bayer Leverkusen \u0111ang l\u00e0 kh\u00e1 cao, theo The Sun, ng\u00f4i sao sinh n\u0103m 1997 \u0111ang \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n r\u1eddi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u01b0\u1edbc \u0110\u1ee9c \u0111\u1ec3 chuy\u1ec3n t\u1edbi Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Arsenal v\u00e0 Chelsea quan t\u00e2m Leon Bailey</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nHLV Maurizio Sarri \u0111ang l\u00ean k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch n\u00e2ng c\u1ea5p \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh, \u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ch\u1ea1y c\u00e1nh ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng. <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/chelsea-tang-gia-hoi-mua-sao-bundesliga-len-70-trieu-bang-172-187291.html\" target=\"_blank\">Chelsea mu\u1ed1n mua Leon Bailey</span> c\u1ee7a Bayer Leverkusen, \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y 58 tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao t\u00e0i n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 21 tu\u1ed5i v\u00e0 mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0a anh v\u1ec1 Stamford Bridge.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"H\u00e0ng hot Bundesliga \u0111\u00e1nh ti\u1ebfng v\u1edbi Chelsea v\u00e0 Arsenal h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" title=\"H\u00e0ng hot Bundesliga \u0111\u00e1nh ti\u1ebfng v\u1edbi Chelsea v\u00e0 Arsenal h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2017/12/26/Leon-Bailey-roi-Bayer-Leverkusen-toi-Ngoai-hang-Anh-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Chelsea v\u00e0 Arsenal quan t\u00e2m Leon Bailey</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nArsenal c\u0169ng l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng quan t\u00e2m c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1997, HLV Emery nh\u1eafm c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Jamaica thay th\u1ebf Danny Welbeck, ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u01b0a v\u00e0o danh s\u00e1ch thanh l\u00fd.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nM\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua, Bailey l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ch\u01a1i t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh Bayer Leverkusen, anh c\u0169ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng ng\u00f4i sao t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t Bundesliga m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba r\u1ed3i.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nC\u1ee5 th\u1ec3, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 21 tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u00e3 ghi t\u1edbi 12 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng c\u00f9ng 6 ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o tr\u00ean m\u1ecdi m\u1eb7t tr\u1eadn, n\u1ebfu t\u00ednh ri\u00eang \u1edf Bundesliga anh c\u00f3 9 b\u00e0n v\u00e0 6 ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o. Bailey s\u1edf h\u1eefu nh\u1eefng k\u1ef9 n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a m\u1ed9t ng\u00f4i sao t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u, anh c\u00f3 t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9, k\u1ef9 thu\u1eadt, kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng s\u00e1ng t\u1ea1o v\u00e0 d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m t\u1ed1t.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNgo\u00e0i ra, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 sinh n\u0103m 1997 c\u00f2n r\u1ea5t \u0111a n\u0103ng, anh c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u1edf c\u1ea3 hai c\u00e1nh, ch\u01a1i \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed h\u1ed9 c\u00f4ng v\u00e0 trung phong c\u1eafm. C\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Jamaica, ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh c\u1ee7a Arsenal ho\u1eb7c Chelsea s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c n\u00e2ng c\u1ea5p \u0111\u00e1ng k\u1ec3.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Bayer Leverkusen gi\u1ea3m gi\u00e1 b\u00e1n Leon Bailey</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Bi\u1ebft \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tin Arsenal v\u00e0 Chelsea quan t\u00e2m Leon Bailey, Bayer Leverkusen \u0111\u00e3 h\u00e9t gi\u00e1 70 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng cho ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. Tuy nhi\u00ean, v\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 21 tu\u1ed5i tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 ra \u0111i, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u01b0\u1edbc \u0110\u1ee9c bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i gi\u1ea3m gi\u00e1 b\u00e1n ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Jamaica.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"H\u00e0ng hot Bundesliga \u0111\u00e1nh ti\u1ebfng v\u1edbi Chelsea v\u00e0 Arsenal h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" title=\"H\u00e0ng hot Bundesliga \u0111\u00e1nh ti\u1ebfng v\u1edbi Chelsea v\u00e0 Arsenal h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2017/12/9/Hang-hot-Bundesliga-danh-tieng-voi-Chelsea-va-Arsenal-hinh-anh-2.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3><span style=\"text-align: justify;\">Bayer Leverkusen \u0111\u00f2i 40 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng cho\u00a0</span>Leon Bailey</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTheo The Sun, Bayer Leverkusen mu\u1ed1n thu v\u1ec1 40 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng t\u1eeb ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n m\u00e0 c\u1ea3 Arsenal v\u00e0 Chelsea \u0111\u1ec1u c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1p \u1ee9ng.\u00a0Nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng hai \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh London s\u1ebd nhanh ch\u00f3ng \u0111\u01b0a ra nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh l\u1ee3i th\u1ebf trong th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u1edbi kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh Leon Bailey ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng trong m\u00f4i tr\u01b0\u1eddng b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 \u1edf Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh, v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 l\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y s\u1ebd t\u1edbi Chelsea hay Arsenal m\u00e0 th\u00f4i.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nL\u00ea H\u01b0\u1eddng (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1603","checkdouble":"191953"},{"date":"08:07 25/07","title":"C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 t\u1eadp c\u00f9ng \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/25/cong-phuong-chan-thuong-khong-the-tap-cung-dt-olympic-viet-nam.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Trong bu\u1ed5i t\u1eadp g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t, C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng d\u00e2y ch\u1eb1ng v\u00e0 ph\u1ea3i nh\u00ecn \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i t\u1ea1i \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam t\u1eadp t\u1eeb b\u00ean ngo\u00e0i s\u00e2n.</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u00f3n nh\u1eadn tin kh\u00f4ng vui khi C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng d\u00e2y ch\u1eb1ng kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 tham gia c\u00f9ng c\u1ea3 \u0111\u1ed9i trong bu\u1ed5i t\u1eadp g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t. C\u00f9ng v\u1edbi C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng, t\u00e2n binh V\u0103n L\u1ee3i c\u0169ng ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ee9ng ngo\u00e0i v\u00ec ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng g\u00e2n kheo.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Cong Phuong chan thuong day chang khien HLV Park Hang Seo lo lang.\" title=\"C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng d\u00e2y ch\u1eb1ng khi\u1ebfn HLV Park Hang Seo lo l\u1eafng.\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/25/cong-phuong-chan-thuong-khong-the-tap-cung-dt-olympic-viet-nam.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng d\u00e2y ch\u1eb1ng khi\u1ebfn HLV Park Hang Seo lo l\u1eafng.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u1ea3 hai \u0111\u1ec1u ch\u1ea1y ch\u1eadm 1 v\u00f2ng s\u00e2n r\u1ed3i ngh\u1ec9 ng\u01a1i, ch\u01b0\u1eddm \u0111\u1ea7u g\u1ed1i b\u1eb1ng \u0111\u00e1. Theo c\u00e1c b\u00e1c s\u0129, C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1ea5t kho\u1ea3ng 2-3 ng\u00e0y \u0111\u1ec3 b\u00ecnh ph\u1ee5c. HLV Park Hang Seo v\u1eabn kh\u00e1 lo l\u1eafng d\u00f9 \u00f4ng g\u1ecdi 7 ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o trong \u0111\u1ee3t t\u1eadp trung l\u1ea7n n\u00e0y.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb cho c\u00fap t\u1ee9 h\u00f9ng<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i, \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam m\u1edbi c\u00f3 17/30 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 l\u00ean t\u1eadp trung, c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i s\u1ebd l\u00ean tuy\u1ec3n mu\u1ed9n v\u00ec b\u1eadn thi \u0111\u1ea5u b\u00e1n k\u1ebft l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111i C\u00fap qu\u1ed1c gia 2018. Trong s\u1ed1 n\u00e0y, 8 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 thu\u1ed9c bi\u00ean ch\u1ebf H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i, SLNA v\u00e0 B\u00ecnh D\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1ed7i \u0111\u1ed9i g\u00f3p m\u1eb7t 2 c\u00e1i t\u00ean, c\u00f2n Thanh H\u00f3a ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n B\u00f9i Ti\u1ebfn D\u0169ng.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam theo k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch s\u1ebd t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i trung t\u00e2m \u0111\u00e0o t\u1ea1o PVF (H\u01b0ng Y\u00ean) cho \u0111\u1ebfn ng\u00e0y 30/7. Sau \u0111\u00f3, c\u1ea3 \u0111\u1ed9i s\u1ebd tr\u1edf v\u1ec1 t\u1eadp t\u1ea1i s\u00e2n M\u1ef9 \u0110\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ec3 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb cho gi\u1ea3i giao h\u1eefu c\u00fap t\u1ee9 h\u00f9ng v\u1edbi ba \u0111\u1ed9i kh\u00e1ch m\u1eddi l\u00e0 U23 Oman, U23 Palestine v\u00e0 U23 Uzbekistan v\u00e0o \u0111\u1ea7u th\u00e1ng 8.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau C\u00fap t\u1ee9 h\u00f9ng, \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam s\u1ebd di chuy\u1ec3n sang Indonesia \u0111\u1ec3 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb cho ASIAD 2018. Hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i, nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c x\u00e1c \u0111\u1ecbnh khi m\u00f4n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 nam ph\u1ea3i b\u1ed1c th\u0103m l\u1ea1i do s\u1ef1 c\u1ed1 &quot;qu\u00ean&quot; UAE v\u00e0 Palestine c\u1ee7a ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 Indonesia trong bu\u1ed5i l\u1ec5 b\u1ed1c th\u0103m \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean.</div>\r\n<h2>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft kh\u00e1c tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn v\u1ec1 \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam:</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/thu-mon-dang-van-lam-khong-nghi-toi-chuyen-thang-thua-khi-len-tuyen-168-191943.html\">Th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n \u0110\u1eb7ng V\u0103n L\u00e2m t\u1ea1o \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u1edbi c\u00e1ch tr\u1ea3 l\u1eddi th\u00f4ng minh khi l\u00ean tuy\u1ec3n</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/doi-thu-mang-luc-luong-rat-manh-sang-doi-dau-u23-viet-nam-tai-cup-tu-hung-168-191940.html\">\u0110\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 mang l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng r\u1ea5t m\u1ea1nh sang \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam t\u1ea1i Cup T\u1ee9 h\u00f9ng</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/van-quyet-khong-ngai-boc-tham-lai-asiad-168-191909.html\">Sao Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam kh\u00f4ng ng\u1ea1i b\u1ed1c th\u0103m l\u1ea1i ASIAD</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/nhat-ban-tiep-tuc-cu-doi-u21-tham-du-asiad-2018-168-191891.html\">\u0110\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c c\u1eed \u0111\u1ed9i U21 tham d\u1ef1 ASIAD 2018</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/gia-ve-xem-u23-viet-nam-thi-dau-co-nguy-co-e-vi-qua-cao-168-191889.html\">Gi\u00e1 v\u00e9 xem U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam thi \u0111\u1ea5u c\u00f3 nguy c\u01a1 b\u1ecb \u1ebf</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/doi-tuyen-viet-nam/nhung-ai-trong-dt-olympic-viet-nam-phai-len-tap-trung-muon-292-191799.html\">Nh\u1eefng ai trong \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam ph\u1ea3i l\u00ean t\u1eadp trung mu\u1ed9n?</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong><br>\r\nN.D (TTVN)</strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1602","checkdouble":"191954"},{"date":"08:38 25/07","title":"\"Welbeck c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 r\u1eddi Arsenal nh\u01b0ng Ramsey th\u00ec kh\u00f4ng\"","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/25/welbeck-co-the-roi-arsenal-nhung-ramsey-thi-khong.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Ray Parlor ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Arsenal, ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u0169 c\u1ee7a Ph\u00e1o th\u1ee7 kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Danny Welbeck c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 r\u1eddi s\u00e2n Emirates c\u00f2n Aaron Ramsey th\u00ec kh\u00f4ng.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Danny Welbeck c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 r\u1eddi Arsenal</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTrong v\u00f2ng 12 th\u00e1ng g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y, Arsenal \u0111\u00e3 chia tay v\u1edbi 3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh, bao g\u1ed3m Alex Oxlade-Chamberlain, Theo Walcott v\u00e0 Jack Wilshere.\u00a0Danny Welbeck \u0111ang l\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh th\u1ee9 4 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 r\u1eddi s\u00e2n Emirates.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Ray Parlor ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Arsenal h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Ray Parlor ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Arsenal h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/13/Ray-Parlor-phat-bieu-ve-Arsenal-hinh-anh.JPG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Danny Welbeck c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 b\u1ecb b\u00e1n \u1edf H\u00e8 2018</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nK\u1ec3 t\u1eeb khi chuy\u1ec3n t\u1edbi Arsenal v\u00e0o n\u0103m 2014, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1990 ch\u01b0a khi n\u00e0o tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh nh\u00e2n t\u1ed1 \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t quan tr\u1ecdng trong l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i c\u1ee7a Ph\u00e1o th\u1ee7. Nh\u1eefng ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u0169ng khi\u1ebfn anh kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u00f3ng g\u00f3p \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u1eb7n cho \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh London.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nHLV Unai Emery kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao t\u00e0i n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a Welbeck, \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha \u0111ang l\u00ean k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch b\u00e1n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 28 tu\u1ed5i \u1edf H\u00e8 2018. <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/voi-15-trieu-bang-welbeck-la-mon-hoi-voi-moi-doi-bong-172-191759.html\" target=\"_blank\">Arsenal\u00a0b\u00e1n Welbeck</span> n\u1ebfu thu v\u1ec1 15 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng, hi\u1ec7n nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng t\u1ea7m trung \u1edf Premier League \u0111ang quan t\u00e2m c\u1ef1u sao M.U.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nRay Parlor ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Arsenal, ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u0169 c\u1ee7a Ph\u00e1o th\u1ee7 kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Danny Welbeck c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 r\u1eddi s\u00e2n Emirates \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ra s\u00e2n nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u201cC\u00f3 th\u1ec3 c\u1eadu \u1ea5y s\u1ebd r\u1eddi Arsenal \u1edf H\u00e8 n\u00e0y. S\u1ef1 c\u1ea1nh tranh v\u1ecb tr\u00ed \u1edf Emirates \u0111ang l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn, \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ra s\u00e2n h\u00e0ng tu\u1ea7n c\u1eadu \u1ea5y bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i ra \u0111i. T\u00f4i ngh\u0129\u00a0Welbeck v\u1eabn c\u1ea7n cho Arsenal, c\u1eadu \u1ea5y l\u00e0 l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn th\u1ee9 5 tr\u00ean h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng sau Aubameyang, Lacazette, Ozil v\u00e0 Mkhitaryan\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u201cTuy nhi\u00ean, c\u00f3 v\u1ebb nh\u01b0 Emery kh\u00f4ng th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 c\u1ea7n Welbeck, Arsenal s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng b\u00e1n c\u1eadu \u1ea5y n\u1ebfu nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb h\u1ee3p l\u00fd. R\u1eddi Emirates l\u00e0 l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn kh\u00f4ng t\u1ed3i v\u1edbi Welbeck, n\u1ebfu t\u00ecm \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed7 h\u1ee3p l\u00fd c\u1eadu \u1ea5y ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ch\u1ee9ng t\u1ecf kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Arsenal kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u00e1n Ramsey</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ray Parlor kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Arsenal c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 b\u00e1n Welbeck nh\u01b0ng h\u1ecd bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i gi\u1eef ch\u00e2n Ramsey, ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u0169 c\u1ee7a Ph\u00e1o th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao t\u00e0i n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi x\u1ee9 Wales.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Welbeck co the roi Arsenal nhung Ramsey thi khong\" title=\"Welbeck c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 r\u1eddi Arsenal nh\u01b0ng Ramsey th\u00ec kh\u00f4ng\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/25/081447-ramsey.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Welbeck c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 r\u1eddi Arsenal nh\u01b0ng Ramsey th\u00ec kh\u00f4ng</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201c\u0110i\u1ec1u quan tr\u1ecdng l\u00e0 Arsenal ph\u1ea3i gi\u1eef Aaron Ramsey, \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t l\u00e0 sau khi \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ec3 Jack Wilshere ra \u0111i. T\u00f4i \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 c\u1eadu \u1ea5y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 trung t\u00e2m xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi \u1edf th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i, c\u1eadu \u1ea5y th\u00edch h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ec3 ch\u01a1i b\u00ean c\u1ea1nh Lucas Torreira\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u201cRamsey c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 cung c\u1ea5p b\u00f3ng th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean cho tuy\u1ebfn tr\u00ean, c\u1eadu \u1ea5y c\u00f3 phong c\u00e1ch thi \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00e0 vai tr\u00f2 kh\u00e1 gi\u1ed1ng v\u1edbi Frank Lampard. Arsenal c\u1ea7n l\u00e0m m\u1ecdi c\u00e1ch \u0111\u1ec3 gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Ramsey, s\u1ebd l\u00e0 sai l\u1ea7m n\u1ebfu h\u1ecd \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1eadu \u1ea5y ra \u0111i\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u01b0\u01a1ng Ng\u00e2n (TTVN)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1601","checkdouble":"191955"},{"date":"08:55 25/07","title":"H\u00e0ng hot Bundesliga \u0111\u00e1nh ti\u1ebfng v\u1edbi Chelsea v\u00e0 Arsenal","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2017/12/9/bailey-danh-tieng-voi-chelsea-va-arsenal.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Leon Bailey r\u1eddi Bayer Leverkusen \u0111ang l\u00e0 kh\u00e1 cao, theo The Sun, ng\u00f4i sao sinh n\u0103m 1997 \u0111ang \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n r\u1eddi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u01b0\u1edbc \u0110\u1ee9c \u0111\u1ec3 chuy\u1ec3n t\u1edbi Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Arsenal v\u00e0 Chelsea quan t\u00e2m Leon Bailey</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nHLV Maurizio Sarri \u0111ang l\u00ean k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch n\u00e2ng c\u1ea5p \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh, \u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ch\u1ea1y c\u00e1nh ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng. <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/chelsea-tang-gia-hoi-mua-sao-bundesliga-len-70-trieu-bang-172-187291.html\" target=\"_blank\">Chelsea mu\u1ed1n mua Leon Bailey</span> c\u1ee7a Bayer Leverkusen, \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y 58 tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao t\u00e0i n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 21 tu\u1ed5i v\u00e0 mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0a anh v\u1ec1 Stamford Bridge.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"H\u00e0ng hot Bundesliga \u0111\u00e1nh ti\u1ebfng v\u1edbi Chelsea v\u00e0 Arsenal h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" title=\"H\u00e0ng hot Bundesliga \u0111\u00e1nh ti\u1ebfng v\u1edbi Chelsea v\u00e0 Arsenal h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2017/12/26/Leon-Bailey-roi-Bayer-Leverkusen-toi-Ngoai-hang-Anh-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Chelsea v\u00e0 Arsenal quan t\u00e2m Leon Bailey</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nArsenal c\u0169ng l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng quan t\u00e2m c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1997, HLV Emery nh\u1eafm c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Jamaica thay th\u1ebf Danny Welbeck, ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u01b0a v\u00e0o danh s\u00e1ch thanh l\u00fd.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nM\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua, Bailey l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ch\u01a1i t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh Bayer Leverkusen, anh c\u0169ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng ng\u00f4i sao t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t Bundesliga m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba r\u1ed3i.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nC\u1ee5 th\u1ec3, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 21 tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u00e3 ghi t\u1edbi 12 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng c\u00f9ng 6 ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o tr\u00ean m\u1ecdi m\u1eb7t tr\u1eadn, n\u1ebfu t\u00ednh ri\u00eang \u1edf Bundesliga anh c\u00f3 9 b\u00e0n v\u00e0 6 ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o. Bailey s\u1edf h\u1eefu nh\u1eefng k\u1ef9 n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a m\u1ed9t ng\u00f4i sao t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u, anh c\u00f3 t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9, k\u1ef9 thu\u1eadt, kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng s\u00e1ng t\u1ea1o v\u00e0 d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m t\u1ed1t.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNgo\u00e0i ra, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 sinh n\u0103m 1997 c\u00f2n r\u1ea5t \u0111a n\u0103ng, anh c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u1edf c\u1ea3 hai c\u00e1nh, ch\u01a1i \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed h\u1ed9 c\u00f4ng v\u00e0 trung phong c\u1eafm. C\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Jamaica, ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh c\u1ee7a Arsenal ho\u1eb7c Chelsea s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c n\u00e2ng c\u1ea5p \u0111\u00e1ng k\u1ec3.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Bayer Leverkusen gi\u1ea3m gi\u00e1 b\u00e1n Leon Bailey</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Bi\u1ebft \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tin Arsenal v\u00e0 Chelsea quan t\u00e2m Leon Bailey, Bayer Leverkusen \u0111\u00e3 h\u00e9t gi\u00e1 70 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng cho ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. Tuy nhi\u00ean, v\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 21 tu\u1ed5i tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 ra \u0111i, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u01b0\u1edbc \u0110\u1ee9c bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i gi\u1ea3m gi\u00e1 b\u00e1n ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Jamaica.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"H\u00e0ng hot Bundesliga \u0111\u00e1nh ti\u1ebfng v\u1edbi Chelsea v\u00e0 Arsenal h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" title=\"H\u00e0ng hot Bundesliga \u0111\u00e1nh ti\u1ebfng v\u1edbi Chelsea v\u00e0 Arsenal h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2017/12/9/Hang-hot-Bundesliga-danh-tieng-voi-Chelsea-va-Arsenal-hinh-anh-2.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3><span style=\"text-align: justify;\">Bayer Leverkusen \u0111\u00f2i 40 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng cho\u00a0</span>Leon Bailey</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTheo The Sun, Bayer Leverkusen mu\u1ed1n thu v\u1ec1 40 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng t\u1eeb ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n m\u00e0 c\u1ea3 Arsenal v\u00e0 Chelsea \u0111\u1ec1u c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1p \u1ee9ng.\u00a0Nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng hai \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh London s\u1ebd nhanh ch\u00f3ng \u0111\u01b0a ra nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh l\u1ee3i th\u1ebf trong th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u1edbi kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh Leon Bailey ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng trong m\u00f4i tr\u01b0\u1eddng b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 \u1edf Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh, v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 l\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y s\u1ebd t\u1edbi Chelsea hay Arsenal m\u00e0 th\u00f4i.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nL\u00ea H\u01b0\u1eddng (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1600","checkdouble":"191957"},{"date":"08:45 25/07","title":"Sao M.U m\u01a1 \u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u00e2n HLV T\u00e2y Ban Nha \u0111\u1ec3 m\u1eaft","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/4/16/mata-muon-tro-lai-dt-tay-ban-nha.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Juan Mata mu\u1ed1n tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i \u0110T T\u00e2y Ban Nha v\u00e0 \u0111\u00e1nh ti\u1ebfng t\u1edbi t\u00e2n HLV Luis Enrique. T\u1eeb n\u0103m 2016 t\u1edbi nay, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 30 tu\u1ed5i kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i kho\u00e1c \u00e1o La Roja.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>\u0110T T\u00e2y Ban Nha thay t\u01b0\u1edbng</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nWorld Cup 2018 ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c l\u00e0 gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u l\u1edbn \u0111\u00e1ng qu\u00ean v\u1edbi \u0110T T\u00e2y Ban Nha. H\u1ecd sa th\u1ea3i HLV Julen Lopetegui ch\u01b0a \u0111\u1ea7y 2 ng\u00e0y tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi ra qu\u00e2n v\u00ec \u0111\u01a1n ph\u01b0\u01a1ng k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Real Madrid.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nVi\u1ec7c Fernando Hierro l\u00ean t\u1ea1m quy\u1ec1n c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng gi\u1ea3i quy\u1ebft v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1. T\u00e2y Ban Nha thi \u0111\u1ea5u b\u1ebft b\u00e1t t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018 v\u00e0 b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i ngay v\u00f2ng 1/8 tr\u01b0\u1edbc ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 Nga. Sau gi\u1ea3i, Hierro \u0111\u00e3 xin r\u00fat lui v\u00e0 gh\u1ebf HLV tr\u01b0\u1edfng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 \u0111\u1ea5u b\u00f2 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c giao l\u1ea1i cho Luis Enrique, c\u1ef1u thuy\u1ec1n tr\u01b0\u1edfng Barcelona.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Juan Mata mu\u1ed1n tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i \u0110T T\u00e2y Ban Nha h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Juan Mata mu\u1ed1n tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i \u0110T T\u00e2y Ban Nha h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/9/Juan-Mata-muon-tro-lai-DT-Tay-Ban-Nha-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Luis Enrique tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh HLV tr\u01b0\u1edfng \u0110T T\u00e2y Ban Nha</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>Mata d\u1ea5y l\u00ean hy v\u1ecdng</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nT\u1eeb n\u0103m 2016 t\u1edbi nay, Juan Mata v\u1eafng m\u1eb7t trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh \u0110T T\u00e2y Ban Nha. Anh kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tham d\u1ef1 c\u1ea3 Euro 2016 l\u1eabn World Cup 2018. Tuy nhi\u00ean, v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a HLV m\u1edbi Enrique, Mata mu\u1ed1n tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i \u0110T T\u00e2y Ban Nha.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201c<em>T\u00f4i ph\u1ea5n kh\u00edch tr\u01b0\u1edbc kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i</em>\u201d, Mata n\u00f3i v\u1edbi ESPN. \u201c<em>T\u00f4i r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng mu\u1ed1n t\u00e1i xu\u1ea5t v\u00e0 c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng ch\u01a1i c\u00e0ng nhi\u1ec1u tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u c\u00e0ng t\u1ed1t cho \u0110TQG. T\u00f4i th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 h\u00e1o h\u1ee9c v\u1ec1 \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3. Nh\u00ecn v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai, \u0110T T\u00e2y Ban Nha c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai t\u01b0\u01a1i s\u00e1ng</em>.\u201d<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"tien ve Mata TBN\" title=\"tien ve Mata TBN\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/25/tien-ve-Mata.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Juan Mata mu\u1ed1n tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i \u0110T T\u00e2y Ban Nha</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201c<em>Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ea1o \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u00e0 nh\u01b0 \u0111\u00e3 n\u00f3i, h\u1ecd c\u00f3 tr\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ed9 \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ea1nh tranh v\u1ecb tr\u00ed. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u0169ng c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u0111\u00e3 tr\u00ean tuy\u1ec3n trong nhi\u1ec1u n\u0103m v\u00e0 c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u kinh nghi\u1ec7m. T\u00f4i ngh\u0129 \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t s\u1ef1 k\u1ebft h\u1ee3p t\u1ed1t v\u00e0 hy v\u1ecdng m\u1ed9t t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai t\u1ed1t \u0111\u1eb9p cho b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 T\u00e2y Ban Nha</em>.\u201d<br>\r\n<br>\r\nMata t\u1edbi nay \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 t\u1ed5ng c\u1ed9ng 41 l\u1ea7n kho\u00e1c \u00e1o v\u00e0 ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 10 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng cho T\u00e2y Ban Nha. Anh ra m\u1eaft v\u00e0o n\u0103m 2009 v\u00e0 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t ph\u1ea7n trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh gi\u00e0nh ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup 2010.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft v\u1ec1 \u0110T T\u00e2y Ban Nha tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/enrique-can-giup-dt-tay-ban-nha-vo-dich-euro-2020-184-191881.html\">Enrique c\u1ea7n gi\u00fap \u0110T T\u00e2y Ban Nha v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch EURO 2020</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/tan-binh-odriozola-tri-an-hlv-lopetegui-trong-ngay-ra-mat-real-180-191566.html\">T\u00e2n binh Odriozola tri \u00e2n HLV Lopetegui trong ng\u00e0y ra m\u1eaft Real</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/luis-enrique-tu-tin-tai-thiet-tay-ban-nha-184-191508.html\">Luis Enrique t\u1ef1 tin t\u00e1i thi\u1ebft T\u00e2y Ban Nha</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nGia Vi (TTVN)<br>\r\n</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1599","checkdouble":"191959"},{"date":"08:41 25/07","title":"Olympic Th\u00e1i Lan \u0111\u0103ng k\u00fd hai c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 g\u1ed1c \u00c2u d\u1ef1 ASIAD","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/2/8/olympic-thai-lan-dang-ky-hai-cau-thu-goc-au-du-asiad.jpeg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>L\u0110B\u0110 Th\u00e1i Lan m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1ed1t danh s\u00e1ch 30 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 s\u1ebd t\u1eadp trung chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb cho ASIAD 2018. \u0110i\u1ec1u b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd l\u00e0 trong s\u1ed1 n\u00e0y c\u00f3 hai g\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1eb7t c\u00f3 g\u1ed1c g\u00e1c ch\u00e2u \u00c2u.</h2><br>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e2y \u00edt ng\u00e0y, L\u0110B\u0110 Th\u00e1i Lan (FAT) \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f4ng b\u1ed1 b\u1ea3n danh s\u00e1ch s\u01a1 b\u1ed9 30 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 t\u1eadp trung \u0110T Olympic Th\u00e1i Lan \u0111\u1ec3 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb cho ASIAD 18 v\u1edbi nhi\u1ec1u b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd th\u00fa v\u1ecb.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">M\u1ed9t trong s\u1ed1 \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 vi\u1ec7c \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 ch\u00f9a V\u00e0ng tri\u1ec7u t\u1eadp hai ng\u00f4i sao c\u00f3 g\u1ed1c g\u00e1c ch\u00e2u \u00c2u l\u00e0 h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 Marco Ballini v\u00e0 ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Oscar Kahl. Ballini mang trong m\u00ecnh hai d\u00f2ng m\u00e1u Italy v\u1edbi Th\u00e1i Lan. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi v\u1ec1 Th\u00e1i Lan thi \u0111\u1ea5u trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o c\u1ee7a CLB Chainat Hornbill, h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 c\u00f3 chi\u1ec1u cao 1m98 n\u00e0y t\u1eebng thi \u0111\u1ea5u cho \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u1ebb c\u1ee7a Cesena (Italia).<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"DT Thai Lan tai ASIAD 2018 se khong dung cau thu tren 23 tuoi.\" title=\"\u0110T Th\u00e1i Lan t\u1ea1i ASIAD 2018 s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng d\u00f9ng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u00ean 23 tu\u1ed5i.\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/5/1/lo-dien-ke-hoach-bat-ngo-cua-dt-thai-lan-tai-asiad-2018.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>\u0110T Th\u00e1i Lan t\u1ea1i ASIAD 2018 s\u1ebd b\u1ed5 sung nhi\u1ec1u g\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1eb7t m\u1edbi</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong khi \u0111\u00f3, Oscar Kahl l\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 mang 2 qu\u1ed1c t\u1ecbch Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n v\u00e0 Th\u00e1i Lan. Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 trung t\u00e2m cao 1m79 n\u00e0y \u0111ang thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u1edf CLB Army United theo b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n t\u1eeb Bangkok United.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">S\u1ef1 b\u1ed5 sung n\u00e0y h\u1ee9a h\u1eb9n s\u1ebd gi\u00fap Th\u00e1i Lan c\u00f3 m\u00e0n l\u1ed9t x\u00e1c so v\u1edbi gi\u1ea3i U23 ch\u00e2u \u00c1 2018, gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u m\u00e0 th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 HLV Worrawoot Srimaka \u0111\u00e3 g\u00e2y th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng khi b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i ngay t\u1eeb v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">So v\u1edbi gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u00f3, l\u1ea7n n\u00e0y \u00f4ng Srimaka c\u0169ng ch\u1ec9 gi\u1eef l\u1ea1i 5 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 trong danh s\u00e1ch t\u1eadp trung \u0111\u1ee3t n\u00e0y, trong \u0111\u00f3 c\u00f3 hai ng\u00f4i sao tri\u1ec3n v\u1ecdng l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng Chenrop Samphaodi v\u00e0 h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 Worawut Namvech. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">M\u1ed9t \u0111i\u1ec1u th\u00fa v\u1ecb kh\u00e1c l\u00e0 m\u1eb7c d\u00f9 m\u00f4n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 nam t\u1ea1i ASIAD 18 quy \u0111\u1ecbnh m\u1ed7i \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u0103ng k\u00fd t\u1ed1i \u0111a 3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u00ean 23 tu\u1ed5i (U23 + 3) nh\u01b0ng Th\u00e1i Lan \u0111\u00e3 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh kh\u00f4ng tri\u1ec7u t\u1eadp c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0o qu\u00e1 23 tu\u1ed5i. Nh\u1eefng t\u00ean tu\u1ed5i nh\u01b0 Chanathip Songkrasin, Teerasil Dangda, Tristan \u0110\u1ed7 \u0111\u1ec1u kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t v\u00e0 h\u1ecd s\u1ebd ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u1edf c\u00e1c CLB thay v\u00ec tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i t\u1eadp trung v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o gi\u1ea3i, ng\u01b0\u1eddi Th\u00e1i c\u0169ng s\u1ebd tham d\u1ef1 gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ee9 h\u00f9ng s\u1ebd di\u1ec5n ra t\u1ea1i Myanmar trong nh\u1eefng ng\u00e0y t\u1edbi. \u0110\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd s\u1ebd l\u00e0 U23 Bahrain, U19 H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c v\u00e0 ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 U23 Myanmar.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<h2>Danh s\u00e1ch tri\u1ec7u t\u00e2p s\u01a1 b\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a \u0110T Olympic Th\u00e1i Lan:<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n: Chakhon Philakhlang, Korraphat Narichan, Nopphon Lakhonphon.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">H\u1eadu v\u1ec7: Worawut Namvech, Jakkit Wachpirom, Apisit Sorada, Saringkan Promsupa, Chartchai Seangdao, Marut Budrak, Patcharapol Intanee, Marco Ballini, Meechok Marhasaranukun, Saranyu Palangwan.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7: Tanasith Siripala, Ratchanat Aranpiroj, Sansern Limwattana, Reungyos Janchaichit, Oscar Kahl, Atthawit Sukchuai, Matee Sarakum, Tanpisit Kukalamo, Nattapon Worasut.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o: Settawut Wongsai, Poramet Arjvirai, Sirimongkhon Jitbanjong, Sihanart Suttisak, Nattawut Suksum, Sittichok Paso, Chenrop Samphaodi, Suksan Mungpao.<span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: &quot;Open Sans&quot;, sans-serif;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1598","checkdouble":"191960"},{"date":"08:41 25/07","title":"\u0110i\u1ec3m tin s\u00e1ng 25/7: Cristiano Ronaldo kh\u1ecfe h\u01a1n c\u1ea3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 20 tu\u1ed5i","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/16/diem-tin-sang-257-cristiano-ronaldo-khoe-hon-ca-cau-thu-20-tuoi.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Cristiano Ronaldo kh\u1ecfe h\u01a1n c\u1ea3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 20 tu\u1ed5i, G\u0110TT Monchi g\u00e2y b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd sau khi b\u1ecb n\u1eabng m\u1ea5t Malcom,... l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c n\u1ed5i b\u1eadt trong m\u1ee5c \u0111i\u1ec3m tin s\u00e1ng ng\u00e0y 25/7.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nh\u1eadn x\u00e9t v\u1ec1 t\u00e2n binh Naby Keita, HLV Jurgen Klopp kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 n\u00e0y ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ch\u01a1i \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed &quot;s\u1ed1 8 s\u00e1ng t\u1ea1o&quot; trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o Liverpool m\u00f9a t\u1edbi.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"\u0110i\u1ec3m tin s\u00e1ng 257 Cristiano Ronaldo kh\u1ecfe h\u01a1n c\u1ea3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 20 tu\u1ed5i h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"\u0110i\u1ec3m tin s\u00e1ng 257 Cristiano Ronaldo kh\u1ecfe h\u01a1n c\u1ea3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 20 tu\u1ed5i h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/16/Nhung-hinh-anh-ve-Cristiano-Ronaldo-toi-Juventus-kiem-tra-y-te-hinh-anh-2.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>Cristiano Ronaldo c\u00f3 n\u1ec1n t\u1ea3ng th\u1ec3 ch\u1ea5t kh\u1ecfe h\u01a1n c\u1ea3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 20 tu\u1ed5i.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTrong bu\u1ed5i ki\u1ec3m tra y t\u1ebf t\u1ea1i Juventus, Cristiano Ronaldo khi\u1ebfn c\u00e1c b\u00e1c s\u0129 t\u1ea1i \u0111\u00e2y b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd khi c\u00f3 n\u1ec1n t\u1ea3ng th\u1ec3 ch\u1ea5t c\u00f2n t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 b\u00ecnh th\u01b0\u1eddng \u1edf \u0111\u1ed9 tu\u1ed5i 20, d\u00f9 si\u00eau sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha \u0111\u00e3 b\u01b0\u1edbc sang tu\u1ed5i 33.&nbsp;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Everton v\u1eeba \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Richarlison t\u1eeb Watford v\u1edbi m\u1ee9c gi\u00e1 l\u00ean \u0111\u1ebfn 40 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng. C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil t\u1eebng ch\u01a1i \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u1edbi 5 b\u00e0n trong 12 tr\u1eadn m\u1edf m\u00e0n m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i cho Watford m\u00f9a tr\u01b0\u1edbc nh\u01b0ng sau \u0111\u00f3 kh\u00f4ng gi\u1eef \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c phong \u0111\u1ed9 \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">L\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong 4 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 qu\u00e1 tu\u1ed5i U23 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tri\u1ec7u t\u1eadp v\u00e0o \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam, Nguy\u1ec5n V\u0103n Quy\u1ebft kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i c\u1ea1nh tranh v\u1edbi c\u00e1c \u0111\u00e0n em \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh su\u1ea5t trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh tham d\u1ef1 ASIAD 2018.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">H\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ed3ng th\u00e0nh ph\u1ed1 Milan cho bi\u1ebft s\u1ebd c\u1ea3i t\u1ea1o s\u00e2n San Siro, n\u01a1i l\u00e0 m\u00e1i nh\u00e0 chung c\u1ee7a Inter v\u00e0 AC Milan. Theo d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn, vi\u1ec7c c\u1ea3i t\u1ea1o s\u1ebd ho\u00e0n t\u1ea5t v\u00e0o n\u0103m 2020.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch Napoli, De Laurentiis kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t c\u00e2u l\u1ea1c b\u1ed9 \u1edf Premier League \u0111\u1eb7t gi\u00e1 100 tri\u1ec7u euro cho Kalidou Koulibaly nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh Naples t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i. CLB h\u1ecfi mua \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c gi\u1edbi truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng cho l\u00e0 Chelsea.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Gi\u00e1m \u0111\u1ed1c th\u1ec3 thao Massimliano Mirabelli b\u1ecb AC Milan sa th\u1ea3i. M\u00f9a tr\u01b0\u1edbc, Mirabelli duy\u1ec7t chi 200 tri\u1ec7u euro \u0111\u1ec3 mua c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 nh\u01b0ng Rossoneri thi \u0111\u1ea5u thi\u1ebfu th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng, kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh su\u1ea5t d\u1ef1 Champions League.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Barcelona chieu mo thanh cong Malcom.\" title=\"Barcelona chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng Malcom.\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/25/chinh-thuc-barcelona-chieu-mo-thanh-cong-malcom.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>Barcelona chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng Malcom.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nB\u1ecb Barcelona n\u1eabng tay tr\u00ean trong v\u1ee5 Malcom, Gi\u00e1m \u0111\u1ed1c th\u1ec3 thao Monchi c\u1ee7a AS Roma kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh s\u1ebd mang v\u1ec1 th\u00e0nh Rome m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 b\u1eb1ng ho\u1eb7c t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n Malcom trong h\u00e8 n\u00e0y.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u01b0\u1edbc nh\u1eefng tin \u0111\u1ed3n v\u1ec1 vi\u1ec7c chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Miralem Pjanic (Juventus), HLV Pep Guardiola kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Man City kh\u00f4ng h\u1ec1 c\u00f3 \u00fd \u0111\u1ecbnh b\u1ed5 sung th\u00eam c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Bosnia trong k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u00e8 n\u00e0y.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chia s\u1ebb v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai Leonardo Bonucci, HLV Gennaro Gattuso th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn trung v\u1ec7 n\u00e0y c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 r\u1eddi AC Milan trong k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u00e8 2018.</div>\r\n<h2>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft \u0111\u00e1ng ch\u00fa \u00fd kh\u00e1c tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn:</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/welbeck-co-the-roi-arsenal-nhung-ramsey-thi-khong-172-191955.html\">Welbeck c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 r\u1eddi Arsenal nh\u01b0ng Ramsey th\u00ec kh\u00f4ng</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/doi-tuyen-viet-nam/cong-phuong-chan-thuong-khong-the-tap-cung-dt-olympic-viet-nam-292-191954.html\">C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 t\u1eadp c\u00f9ng \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/danh-sach-cau-thu-hay-nhat-nam-cua-fifa-mbappe-sanh-vai-cung-ronaldo-messi-184-191953.html\">Danh s\u00e1ch c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 hay nh\u1ea5t n\u0103m c\u1ee7a FIFA: Mbappe s\u00e1nh vai c\u00f9ng Ronaldo, Messi</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-italia/khong-du-dau-cung-juventus-cristiano-ronaldo-sang-trung-quoc-quang-ba-thuong-hieu-176-191950.html\">Kh\u00f4ng du \u0111\u1ea5u c\u00f9ng Juventus, Ronaldo sang Trung Qu\u1ed1c qu\u1ea3ng b\u00e1 th\u01b0\u01a1ng hi\u1ec7u</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-italia/chinh-thuc-as-roma-chieu-mo-thanh-cong-robin-olsen-176-191948.html\">CH\u00cdNH TH\u1ee8C: AS Roma \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi thay th\u1ebf Alisson v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 ch\u1ec9 b\u1eb1ng 1/8</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/chinh-thuc-barcelona-chieu-mo-thanh-cong-malcom-180-191946.html\">CH\u00cdNH TH\u1ee8C: Barcelona c\u01b0\u1edbp th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng Malcom tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u0169i AS Roma</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>T\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p (TTVN)</strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1597","checkdouble":"191962"},{"date":"08:42 25/07","title":"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh BATE Borisov vs HJK Helsinki 00h00 ng\u00e0y 26/7 (Champions League 2018/19)","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/7/25/nhan-dinh-bate-borisov-vs-hjk-helsinki-00h00-ngay-267-champions-league-201819.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>BATE Borisov vs HJK Helsinki l\u00fac 00h00 ng\u00e0y 26/7 (V\u00f2ng s\u01a1 lo\u1ea1i c\u00fap C1/Champions League 2018/19)): Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1, \u00fd ki\u1ebfn chuy\u00ean gia, d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3, ph\u00e2n t\u00edch chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n, c\u00e1c th\u00f4ng tin, th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea b\u00ean l\u1ec1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u.</h2><div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh BATE Borisov vs HJK Helsinki 00h00 ng\u00e0y 267 c\u00fap C1 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh BATE Borisov vs HJK Helsinki 00h00 ng\u00e0y 267 c\u00fap C1 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/25/BATE-Borisov-vs-HJK-Helsinki.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">BATE Borisov vs HJK Helsinki</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<h2 style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/nhan-dinh-bong-da-c344-p1.html\" target=\"_blank\">Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1</span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span> </span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span>BATE Borisov vs HJK Helsinki: 2-0<br>\r\n</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></h2>\r\n<div>D\u00f9 \u0111\u1ebfn t\u1eeb n\u1ec1n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 trung b\u00ecnh y\u1ebfu t\u1ea1i ch\u00e2u \u00c2u (Belarus), nh\u01b0ng BATE Borisov kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 xa l\u1ea1 khi tr\u00ean 5 l\u1ea7n g\u00f3p m\u1eb7t t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng Champions League, g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2015/16. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 m\u00f9a b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1ng nh\u1edb v\u1edbi th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Alyaksandr Yermakovich, khi h\u1ecd ki\u1ebfm \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 4/6 \u0111i\u1ec3m t\u1ed1i \u0111a t\u1eeb tay \u00f4ng l\u1edbn AS Roma. Ti\u1ebfc l\u00e0 BATE Borisov \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh v\u00e9 \u0111i ti\u1ebfp v\u00ec k\u00e9m \u0111\u1ed9i nh\u00ec b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u00fang 1 \u0111i\u1ec3m.\u00a0 <br>\r\n<br>\r\nTrong khi \u0111\u00f3, ti\u1ebfng l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng s\u1ed1 1 t\u1ea1i Ph\u1ea7n Lan, nh\u01b0ng k\u1ec3 t\u1eeb sau m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 1998/99, HJK Helsinki kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n g\u00f3p m\u1eb7t t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ea5p CLB\u00a0danh gi\u00e1 nh\u1ea5t h\u00e0nh tnh. L\u1ea7n g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t tham d\u1ef1 v\u00f2ng s\u01a1 lo\u1ea1i Champions League (2015/16), HJK Helsinki b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng s\u01a1 lo\u1ea1i th\u1ee9 3.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nM\u00f9a n\u00e0y, HJK Helsinki ph\u1ea3i xu\u1ea5t ph\u00e1t t\u1eeb v\u00f2ng s\u01a1 lo\u1ea1i th\u1ee9 nh\u1ea5t v\u00e0 gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng v\u1edbi t\u1ed5ng t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 5-2. T\u00ednh tr\u00ean m\u1ecdi m\u1eb7t tr\u1eadn, HJK Helsinki \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1ea3i qua 5 tr\u1eadn li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp kh\u00f4ng th\u1eafng theo TLCA. Tr\u00ean s\u00e2n kh\u00e1ch, con s\u1ed1 \u1ea5y l\u00e0 7 (h\u00f2a 2, thua 5).<br>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u1edbi t\u01b0\u01a1ng quan nh\u01b0 v\u1eady, kh\u00f4ng nhi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1eddi tin v\u00e0o kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng t\u1ea1o ra b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd t\u1eeb ph\u00eda \u0111\u1ed9i kh\u00e1ch. Ch\u00ednh v\u00ec v\u1eady, BATE Borisov \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 r\u1ea5t cao.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTH\u00c0NH T\u00cdCH \u0110\u1ed0I \u0110\u1ea6U<br>\r\n- Hai \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u00e3 g\u1eb7p nhau t\u1ed5ng c\u1ed9ng 1 tr\u1eadn, BATE Borisov th\u1eafng 0, h\u00f2a 1, thua 0.<br>\r\n- Tr\u00ean s\u00e2n c\u1ee7a BATE Borisov, 2 \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u01b0a t\u1eebng g\u1eb7p nhau. </div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1596","checkdouble":"191963"},{"date":"21:36 24/07","title":"Chelsea l\u00ean k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 sao Bayern","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/24/chelsea-len-ke-hoach-chieu-mo-sao-bayern.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Chelsea nh\u1eafm chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Thiago Alcantara \u1edf k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u00e8 2018 nh\u1eb1m gia c\u1ed1 s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh cho h\u00e0ng ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7.</h2><h2>Chelsea mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 Thiago</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo nhi\u1ec1u ngu\u1ed3n tin, Bayern Munich \u0111ang mong mu\u1ed1n chia tay ng\u00f4i sao 27 tu\u1ed5i. HLV Niko Kovac d\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ecbnh s\u1ebd c\u1eaft g\u1ecdt \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh \u0111\u00e1ng k\u1ec3 \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean n\u1eafm quy\u1ec1n t\u1ea1i Allianz Arena.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nThiago Alcantara \u0111\u00e3 \u1edf r\u1ea5t g\u1ea7n Man United h\u1ed3i n\u0103m 2013. Nh\u01b0ng HLV Pep Guardiola \u0111\u00e3 thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha t\u1edbi \u0110\u1ee9c thi \u0111\u1ea5u.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Thiago Alcantara\" title=\"Thiago Alcantara\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/24/chelsea-len-ke-hoach-chieu-mo-sao-bayern.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Chelsea nh\u1eafm chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Thiago Alcantara</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nMan City \u0111\u00e3 theo d\u00f5i Thiago s\u00e1t sao trong v\u00f2ng 12 th\u00e1ng qua. Nh\u01b0ng t\u1edd ESPN kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Chelsea v\u00e0 Man United b\u00e2y gi\u1edd c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 nh\u1ea3y v\u00e0o cu\u1ed9c.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nBayern Munich kh\u00e1 c\u1edfi m\u1edf trong vi\u1ec7c \u0111\u1ec3 m\u1ed9t v\u00e0i c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ra \u0111i. V\u1edbi 9 ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh, HLV Kovac c\u0169ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 tho\u1ea3i m\u00e1i \u0111\u1ec3 Thiago ra \u0111i.</div>\r\n<h2>Bayern c\u0169ng mu\u1ed1n b\u00e1n Thiago</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha \u0111\u00e3 g\u1eb7p kh\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng k\u1ec3 t\u1eeb khi chuy\u1ec3n t\u1edbi s\u00e2n Allianz Arena. D\u1eabu v\u1eady, anh v\u1eabn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c coi l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 t\u00e0i n\u0103ng nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi. Do \u0111\u00f3, \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u1eef k\u00fd c\u1ee7a Thiago, c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i chi kho\u1ea3ng 50 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u1ea3 Chelsea v\u00e0 Man United \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u00e3 chi ti\u00eau kh\u00e1 m\u1ea1nh tay \u0111\u1ec3 t\u0103ng c\u01b0\u1eddng tuy\u1ebfn ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 h\u00e8 n\u00e0y. Jorginho \u0111\u00e3 chuy\u1ec3n t\u1edbi Stamford Bridge v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 52 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng. Trong khi \u0111\u00f3, Fred gia nh\u1eadp Man United v\u1edbi s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u01b0\u1edbc t\u00ednh l\u00e0 47 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u00e1c \u0111\u1ea1i gia n\u01b0\u1edbc Anh d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn s\u1ebd c\u00f2n \u0111\u1ed1i di\u1ec7n v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 c\u1ea1nh tranh kh\u1ed1c li\u1ec7t t\u1edbi t\u1eeb Barcelona. G\u00e3 kh\u1ed5ng l\u1ed3 x\u1ee9 Catalan c\u0169ng mong m\u1ecfi \u0111\u01b0a ng\u00f4i sao 27 tu\u1ed5i tr\u1edf v\u1ec1 m\u00e1i nh\u00e0 Camp Nou sau 5 n\u0103m thi \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ea1i \u0110\u1ee9c.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng kh\u00e1c:</strong><br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/diem-tin-bong-da-24h-toi-ngay-247-mu-nham-sao-tuyen-croatia-184-191937.html\">\u0110i\u1ec3m tin B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 24h t\u1ed1i ng\u00e0y 24/7: MU nh\u1eafm sao tuy\u1ec3n Croatia</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/tin-chuyen-nhuong/3-thuong-vu-co-the-se-no-tai-man-united-trong-nhung-ngay-toi-187-191935.html\">3 th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 s\u1ebd n\u1ed5 t\u1ea1i Man United trong nh\u1eefng ng\u00e0y t\u1edbi</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xu\u00e2n Phong (TTVN)</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1595","checkdouble":"191939"},{"date":"21:19 24/07","title":"\u0110\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 mang l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng r\u1ea5t m\u1ea1nh sang \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam t\u1ea1i Cup T\u1ee9 h\u00f9ng","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/24/doi-thu-mang-luc-luong-rat-manh-sang-doi-dau-u23-viet-nam-tai-cup-tu-hung.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>\u0110\u1ec3 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb cho ASIAD 2018, \u0110T U23 Palestine c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 mang m\u1ed9t l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng r\u1ea5t m\u1ea1nh sang tham d\u1ef1 gi\u1ea3i t\u1ee9 h\u00f9ng c\u00f9ng \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam.</h2><h2>U23 Palestine mang l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng r\u1ea5t m\u1ea1nh sang \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"U23 Palestine mang l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng r\u1ea5t m\u1ea1nh sang \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"U23 Palestine mang l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng r\u1ea5t m\u1ea1nh sang \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/24/nhan-dinh-u23-qatar-vs-u23-palestine-15h00-ngay-19-1-tu-ket-vck-u23-chau-a-2018.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>\u0110T U23 Palestine mang l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng kh\u00e1 m\u1ea1nh sang Vi\u1ec7t Nam</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nh\u1eadn l\u1eddi m\u1eddi t\u1eeb VFF, \u0110T U23 Palestine s\u1ebd mang l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng m\u1ea1nh nh\u1ea5t sang tham d\u1ef1 gi\u1ea3i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 qu\u1ed1c t\u1ebf - C\u00fap VinaPhone 2018. Gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u n\u0103m nay 3 \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n r\u1ea5t m\u1ea1nh t\u1ea1i ch\u00e2u l\u1ee5c l\u00e0 U23 Oman, U23 Palestine, U23 Uzbekistan c\u00f9ng ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 \u0110T U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u01b0\u1ee3c bi\u1ebft, x\u00e1c \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u00e2y s\u1ebd d\u1ecbp quan tr\u1ecdng \u0111\u1ec3 th\u1eed nghi\u1ec7m \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi v\u00e0o v\u00e0o ASIAD n\u00ean U23 Palestine mang theo qu\u00e2n s\u1ed1 kh\u00e1 m\u1ea1nh g\u1ed3m nhi\u1ec1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 t\u1eebng tham d\u1ef1 VCK U23 ch\u00e2u \u00c1 v\u1eeba qua nh\u01b0 th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh Abuaker, Fahkouri, h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 Alashhab, Farawi, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Abuwada, Fannoun, Dabbagh, ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Yousef, Qymbor&hellip;<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t, trong chuy\u1ebfn sang Vi\u1ec7t Nam l\u1ea7n n\u00e0y, \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh c\u1ee7a U23 Palestine c\u00f2n c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 g\u00f3p m\u1eb7t c\u1ee7a b\u1ed9 \u0111\u00f4i c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111ang thi \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ea1i Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n l\u00e0 h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 Termanini (AFC Eskilstuna) v\u00e0 ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 El-Kayed (CLB Prespa Birlik).<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1edbi l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng kh\u00e1 \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ec1u v\u1edbi nhi\u1ec1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 cao to, U23 Palestine \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 l\u00e0 thu\u1ed1c th\u1eed li\u1ec1u cao v\u1edbi U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o tranh t\u00e0i t\u1ea1i ASIAD. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u1ea1i VCK U23 ch\u00e2u \u00c1 v\u1eeba qua, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng T\u00e2y \u00c1 n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 thi \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u00e1 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u00e0 l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o t\u1edbi v\u00f2ng t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft gi\u1ea3i U23 ch\u00e2u \u00c1 2018. \u0110\u00e2y c\u0169ng ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e3 v\u00f9i d\u1eadp U23 Th\u00e1i Lan v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 5-1, d\u00f9 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Th\u00e1i v\u1eeba v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch SEA Games 28. Do \u0111\u00f3, U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ph\u00e9p coi th\u01b0\u1eddng \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y. V\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c mang t\u1edbi H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ea7y \u0111\u1ee7 anh h\u00e0o, U23 Palestine h\u1ee9a h\u1eb9n s\u1ebd l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00e1ng g\u1eddm&nbsp;t\u1ea1i Gi\u1ea3i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 qu\u1ed1c t\u1ebf U23 s\u1eafp t\u1edbi.</p>\r\n<h2>Danh s\u00e1ch \u0110T U23 Palestine :</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u01b0\u1edfng \u0111o\u00e0n : Islam M.A.Masharqa</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">HLV tr\u01b0\u1edfng : Ayman R.K.Sangdouqa</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u1ee3 l\u00fd HLV tr\u01b0\u1edfng : Husam.I.A.Younis, Osama K.M.Abualla, Anan W.A.Saleh</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">B\u00e1c s\u0129 v\u1eadt l\u00fd tr\u1ecb li\u1ec7u : Mustafa M.A.Maree</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u00e1n b\u1ed9 ph\u1ee5c v\u1ee5 : Mohammed T.S.Asmar</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 (20 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7) :</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Naim R.N.Abuaker, Ramzi S.A.Fahkouri, Ahmad M.A.Qatmish, Mahmoud M.N.Abuwarda, Mohanad S.A.Fannoun, Mahmoud A.N.Yousef, Yousef M.M.Alashhab, Mohammed A.A.Obaid, Mousa B.M.Farawi, Hani S.A.Abdallah, Oday I.M.Dabbagh, Shehab R.I.Qymbor, Mohammed H.M.Alassa, Mohammed A.M.Khalil, Mohammed B.A.Rashid, Saato Ampntel Salam Fouflias, Michel Milad Termanini, Mohammad El-Kayed, Omar El Cherif, Mohammed A.I.Afmed.</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/nhat-ban-tiep-tuc-cu-doi-u21-tham-du-asiad-2018-168-191891.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/24/nhat-ban-tiep-tuc-cu-doi-u21-tham-du-asiad-2018.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/nhat-ban-tiep-tuc-cu-doi-u21-tham-du-asiad-2018-168-191891.html\">\u0110\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c c\u1eed \u0111\u1ed9i U21 tham d\u1ef1 ASIAD 2018</span><br>\r\nN\u1ebfu k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 b\u1ed1c th\u0103m kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u s\u1ef1 x\u00e1o tr\u1ed9n, nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u \u0111\u1ed9i U21 Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng ASIAD 2018.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/doi-tuyen-viet-nam/le-boc-tham-lai-bong-da-nam-asiad-2018-dien-ra-vao-ngay-nao-292-191911.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/24/le-boc-tham-lai-bong-da-nam-asiad-2018-dien-ra-vao-ngay-nao.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/doi-tuyen-viet-nam/le-boc-tham-lai-bong-da-nam-asiad-2018-dien-ra-vao-ngay-nao-292-191911.html\">L\u1ec5 b\u1ed1c th\u0103m l\u1ea1i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 nam ASIAD 2018 di\u1ec5n ra v\u00e0o ng\u00e0y n\u00e0o?</span><br>\r\nL\u1ec5 b\u1ed1c th\u0103m l\u1ea1i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 nam ASIAD 2018 kh\u00f4ng di\u1ec5n ra t\u1ea1i n\u01b0\u1edbc ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 Indonesia m\u00e0 \u1edf tr\u1ee5 s\u1edf c\u1ee7a Li\u00ean \u0111o\u00e0n B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00e2u \u00c1 \u1edf Kuala Lumpur (Malaysia).</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/boc-tham-asiad-2018-khi-phep-vua-cung-phai-thua-le-lang-168-191908.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/5/30/boc-tham-asiad-2018-khi-phep-vua-cung-phai-thua-le-lang.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/boc-tham-asiad-2018-khi-phep-vua-cung-phai-thua-le-lang-168-191908.html\">B\u1ed1c th\u0103m ASIAD 2018: Khi ph\u00e9p vua c\u0169ng ph\u1ea3i thua l\u1ec7 l\u00e0ng</span><br>\r\nCh\u01b0a \u0111\u1ea7y m\u1ed9t th\u00e1ng n\u1eefa ASIAD 2018 s\u1ebd ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c kh\u1edfi tranh song cho t\u1edbi th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m n\u00e0y, n\u01b0\u1edbc ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 Indonesia v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a th\u1ec3 ch\u1ed1t k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch b\u1ed1c th\u0103m l\u1ea1i m\u00f4n b\u00f3ng...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)<o:p></o:p></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1594","checkdouble":"191940"},{"date":"21:33 24/07","title":"\u0110T Olympic Indonesia \u0111\u1eb7t m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau r\u1ea5t cao t\u1ea1i ASIAD 2018","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2017/8/20/dt-olympic-indonesia-dat-muc-tieu-rat-cao-tai-asiad-2018.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>\u0110\u1ebfn l\u00fac n\u00e0y, c\u00f4ng t\u00e1c chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng M.U ch\u01b0a nh\u01b0 mong mu\u1ed1n c\u1ee7a HLV Jose Mourinho. \u00d4ng mu\u1ed1n Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf c\u00f3 th\u00eam \u00edt nh\u1ea5t 2 t\u00e2n binh ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng n\u1eefa.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>M.U chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng ch\u01b0a t\u1ed1t</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nMan United \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 3 t\u00e2n binh tr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u1ec1m m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi 2018/19. Tuy nhi\u00ean, trong \u0111\u00f3 th\u1ef1c ch\u1ea5t ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 Fred l\u00e0 b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng l\u1edbn v\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n s\u1ebd c\u00f3 t\u1ea7m \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng t\u1edbi Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf trong th\u1eddi gian t\u1edbi. C\u00f2n h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 c\u00e1nh Diogo Dalot v\u00e0 th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh Lee Grant ho\u1eb7c qu\u00e1 non n\u1edbt ho\u1eb7c qu\u00e1 l\u1edbn tu\u1ed5i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nHi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i, M.U \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho l\u00e0 \u0111ang c\u00f3 li\u00ean h\u1ec7 v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng Harry Maguire, Miralem Pjanic v\u00e0 Ivan Perisic. Trung v\u1ec7, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 trung t\u00e2m c\u1ed9ng th\u00eam t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng c\u00e1nh l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng g\u00ec HLV Jose Mourinho y\u00eau c\u1ea7u b\u1ed9 ph\u1eadn chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng M.U b\u1ed5 sung cho m\u00ecnh.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Mourinho mu\u1ed1n chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng MU c\u00f3 th\u00eam 2 t\u00e2n binh h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Mourinho mu\u1ed1n chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng MU c\u00f3 th\u00eam 2 t\u00e2n binh h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/21/Mourinho-muon-chuyen-nhuong-MU-co-them-2-tan-binh-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">M.U m\u1edbi c\u00f3 ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Fred l\u00e0 \u0111\u00e1ng ch\u00fa \u00fd</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>Mourinho ra y\u00eau c\u1ea7u</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTrong m\u1ed9t cu\u1ed9c tr\u1ea3 l\u1eddi ph\u1ecfng v\u1ea5n m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, Mourinho kh\u00f4ng ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 c\u1ee5 th\u1ec3 c\u1ea7n nh\u1eefng ai, song g\u1ee3i \u00fd r\u1eb1ng ch\u01b0a ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1edbi c\u00f4ng t\u00e1c chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u1ebfn l\u00fac n\u00e0y.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cT\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t chuy\u1ec7n\u201d, \u00f4ng n\u00f3i v\u1edbi ESPN. \u201cNh\u1eefng g\u00ec \u0111\u00e3 x\u1ea3y ra ch\u01b0a h\u1eb3n \u0111\u00e3 nh\u01b0 v\u1eady. V\u00e0 l\u00fac n\u00e0y, t\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 th\u00eam 2 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 m\u1edbi n\u1eefa.\u201d<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Mourinho\" title=\"HLV Mourinho\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/24/HLV-Mourinho.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>HLV Mourinho ra y\u00eau c\u1ea7u v\u1ec1 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng M.U</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nChi\u1ec1u s\u00e2u \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh c\u1ee7a M.U s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ki\u1ec3m ch\u1ee9ng sau ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u1ee7a h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 Antonio Valencia. S\u1eafp t\u1edbi, h\u1ecd s\u1ebd l\u1ea7n l\u01b0\u1ee3t g\u1eb7p AC Milan, Liverpool v\u00e0 Real Madrid t\u1ea1i gi\u1ea3i giao h\u1eefu International Champions Cup tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t M\u1ef9.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTr\u01b0\u1edbc Valencia, t\u00e0i n\u0103ng tr\u1ebb Dalot c\u0169ng ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng ngh\u1ec9 t\u1edbi th\u00e1ng 9 c\u00f2n Matteo Darmian nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng s\u1ebd tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i Serie A. \u201cT\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng ngh\u0129 Valencia s\u1ebd k\u1ecbp g\u00f3p m\u1eb7t \u1edf 3 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1edbi\u201d, Mourinho n\u00f3i th\u00eam. \u201c\u0110\u00e2y kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i l\u00fac ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn nh\u1eefng r\u1ee7i ro.\u201d<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cValencia kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u1eadu b\u00e9 n\u1eefa. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i ph\u1ea3i c\u1ea9n tr\u1ecdng v\u1edbi c\u1eadu \u1ea5y v\u00e0 gi\u00fap c\u1eadu \u1ea5y s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng cho m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 mua v\u1ec1 m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi. Dalot m\u1edbi 19 tu\u1ed5i song l\u00e0 h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 ph\u1ea3i t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t \u1edf \u0111\u1ed9 tu\u1ed5i c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. Nh\u01b0ng c\u1eadu \u1ea5y m\u1edbi ph\u1ea3i ph\u1eabu thu\u1eadt v\u00e0 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u00e0ng ph\u1ea3i c\u1ea9n th\u1eadn v\u1edbi Valencia.\u201d<br>\r\n<strong><br>\r\nXem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft v\u1ec1 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng M.U tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/tin-chuyen-nhuong/3-thuong-vu-co-the-se-no-tai-man-united-trong-nhung-ngay-toi-187-191935.html\">3 th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 s\u1ebd n\u1ed5 t\u1ea1i Man United trong nh\u1eefng ng\u00e0y t\u1edbi</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/mu-nhan-tin-buon-tu-muc-tieu-so-1-172-191932.html\">M.U nh\u1eadn tin bu\u1ed3n t\u1eeb m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau s\u1ed1 1</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-italia/hlv-gattuso-muon-bonucci-o-lai-milan-176-191897.html\">HLV Milan n\u00f3i g\u00ec khi Bonucci c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 sang M.U ho\u1eb7c Real?</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/mourinho-noi-gi-ve-viec-mu-chi-50-trieu-bang-mua-alderweireld-172-191725.html\">Mourinho n\u00f3i g\u00ec v\u1ec1 vi\u1ec7c MU chi 50 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng mua Alderweireld?</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nGia Vi (TTVN)</strong><br>\r\n\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1593","checkdouble":"191941"},{"date":"22:54 24/07","title":"B\u1ed9 \u0111\u00f4i sao tr\u1ebb MU tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng \u1edf ICC 2018","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/24/bo-doi-sao-tre-mu-tuyen-bo-san-sang-toa-sang-o-icc-2018.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>B\u1ed9 \u0111\u00f4i sao tr\u1ebb Axel Tuanzebe v\u00e0 Timothy Fosu-Mensah quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m ch\u1ee9ng t\u1ecf t\u00e0i n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh \u1edf tour du \u0111\u1ea5u h\u00e8 2018 c\u1ee7a Man United.</h2><h2>Tuanzebe quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m cao \u0111\u1ed9</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trung v\u1ec7 tr\u1ebb 20 tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i \u1edf 2 tr\u1eadn giao h\u1eefu \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean c\u1ee7a Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t M\u1ef9. Anh v\u1eabn c\u00f2n c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec3 ch\u1ee9ng t\u1ecf m\u00ecnh \u1edf c\u00e1c tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi AC Milan, Liverpool, Real Madrid v\u00e0 Bayern Munich tr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u1ec1m chi\u1ebfn d\u1ecbch Premier League.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u1ede m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u0103m ngo\u00e1i, Tuanzebe \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c g\u1eedi t\u1edbi Aston Villa thi \u0111\u1ea5u theo d\u1ea1ng cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n. Anh ph\u1ea3i tr\u1edf v\u1ec1 s\u00e2n Old Trafford sau khi g\u1eb7p ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1eaft c\u00e1 h\u1ed3i th\u00e1ng 4. V\u00e0 sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi San Jose Earthquakes, Tuanzebe t\u1ecf ra kh\u00e1 h\u00e0o h\u1ee9ng:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"B\u1ed9 \u0111\u00f4i sao tr\u1ebb MU tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng \u1edf ICC 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"B\u1ed9 \u0111\u00f4i sao tr\u1ebb MU tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng \u1edf ICC 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/24/bo-doi-sao-tre-mu-tuyen-bo-san-sang-toa-sang-o-icc-2018.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Sao tr\u1ebb MU quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n \u1edf ICC 2018</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<em>\u201c\u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t bu\u1ed5i t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n t\u1ed1t. Tinh th\u1ea7n c\u1ee7a to\u00e0n \u0111\u1ed9i l\u00fac n\u00e0y \u0111ang r\u1ea5t ph\u1ea5n ch\u1ea5n. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb trong \u0111\u1ed9i v\u00e0 t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ec1u gi\u00e0u n\u0103ng l\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u00e0o l\u00fac n\u00e0y. Th\u1eadt t\u1ed1t khi t\u00f4i c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i ra s\u00e2n \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean k\u1ec3 t\u1eeb khi tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i sau ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng. T\u00f4i c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y t\u1ed1t v\u00e0 \u0111\u00e3 s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng chi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ea5u h\u1ebft m\u00ecnh.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cT\u00f4i th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i ra s\u00e2n nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n \u0111\u1ec3 ch\u1ee9ng t\u1ecf m\u00ecnh c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u00e0m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c g\u00ec. Khi tr\u01b0\u1edfng th\u00e0nh trong th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u b\u1ea1n ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ed1i m\u1eb7t. B\u1ea1n ph\u1ea3i ch\u1ee9ng t\u1ecf v\u1edbi th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi nh\u1eefng g\u00ec m\u00ecnh c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u00e0m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c\u201d.</em></div>\r\n<h2>Fosu-Mensah hy v\u1ecdng thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Mourinho</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t n\u0103m thi \u0111\u1ea5u theo d\u1ea1ng cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n kh\u00e1 t\u1ed1t t\u1ea1i Crystal Palace. Ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi H\u00e0 Lan \u0111\u00e3 ra s\u00e2n 24 l\u1ea7n cho \u201c\u0110\u1ea1i b\u00e0ng\u201d v\u00e0 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t ph\u1ea7n c\u1ee7a h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 Palace tr\u1ee5 h\u1ea1ng th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng \u1edf Premier League.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<em>\u201cCh\u01a1i \u1edf Palace m\u00f9a tr\u01b0\u1edbc mang l\u1ea1i cho t\u00f4i nh\u1eefng kinh nghi\u1ec7m t\u1ed1t. Th\u1eadt tuy\u1ec7t khi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u01a1i \u1edf Premier League. T\u00f4i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c h\u1ecdc h\u1ecfi r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u t\u1eeb HLV Roy Hodgson.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cB\u00e2y gi\u1edd t\u00f4i th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 mu\u1ed1n tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh m\u1ed9t ph\u1ea7n c\u1ee7a Man United. T\u00f4i mong mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c h\u1ecdc h\u1ecfi, thi \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00e0 ph\u00e1t tri\u1ec3n d\u01b0\u1edbi s\u1ef1 d\u1eabn d\u1eaft c\u1ee7a Mourinho v\u00e0 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh m\u1ed9t ph\u1ea7n c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng hi\u1ec7n nay\u201d.</em><br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c kh\u00e1c v\u1ec1 Man United:</strong><br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/diem-tin-bong-da-24h-toi-ngay-247-mu-nham-sao-tuyen-croatia-184-191937.html\">\u0110i\u1ec3m tin B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 24h t\u1ed1i ng\u00e0y 24/7: MU nh\u1eafm sao tuy\u1ec3n Croatia</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/nhung-van-de-cua-mu-sau-tran-hoa-nhat-san-jose-earthquakes-172-191926.html\">Nh\u1eefng v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 c\u1ee7a MU sau tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a nh\u1ea1t San Jose Earthquakes</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xu\u00e2n Phong (TTVN)</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1592","checkdouble":"191942"},{"date":"21:48 24/07","title":"Th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n \u0110\u1eb7ng V\u0103n L\u00e2m t\u1ea1o \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u1edbi c\u00e1ch tr\u1ea3 l\u1eddi th\u00f4ng minh khi l\u00ean tuy\u1ec3n","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/24/thu-mon-dang-van-lam-khong-nghi-toi-chuyen-thang-thua-khi-len-tuyen.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Chia s\u1ebb sau bu\u1ed5i t\u1eadp c\u1ee7a \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam, th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n \u0110\u1eb7ng V\u0103n L\u00e2m kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh kh\u00f4ng coi c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 trong vi\u1ec7c c\u1ea1nh tranh su\u1ea5t tham d\u1ef1 ASIAD 2018.</h2><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">H\u1ed3i \u0111\u1ea7u th\u00e1ng 7 v\u1eeba qua, L\u0110B\u0110 Vi\u1ec7t Nam VFF \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f4ng b\u1ed1 danh s\u00e1ch t\u1eadp trung \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb cho ASIAD 2018. Tuy nhi\u00ean \u0111\u00e2y m\u1edbi ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 danh s\u00e1ch s\u01a1 b\u1ed9 v\u00e0 nhi\u1ec7m v\u1ee5 c\u1ee7a HLV Park Hang Seo trong nh\u1eefng ng\u00e0y t\u1edbi l\u00e0 l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn ra 20 g\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1eb7t \u01b0u t\u00fa nh\u1ea5t trong danh s\u00e1ch 30 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c g\u1ecdi \u0111\u1ec3 l\u00ean \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng sang Indonesia d\u1ef1 gi\u1ea3i.<br />\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n \u0110\u1eb7ng V\u0103n L\u00e2m kh\u00f4ng ngh\u0129 t\u1edbi chuy\u1ec7n th\u1eafng thua khi l\u00ean tuy h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n \u0110\u1eb7ng V\u0103n L\u00e2m kh\u00f4ng ngh\u0129 t\u1edbi chuy\u1ec7n th\u1eafng thua khi l\u00ean tuy h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/24/dmh8243-15324411028441950395411.jpg\" /></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>Th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n \u0110\u1eb7ng V\u0103n L\u00e2m - \u1ea2nh: D\u00e2n Tr\u00ed</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u1ede v\u1ecb tr\u00ed th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n V\u0103n L\u00e2m s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i c\u1ea1nh tranh v\u1edbi c\u00e1c \u2018\u0111\u00e0n em\u2019 B\u00f9i Ti\u1ebfn D\u0169ng v\u00e0 Nguy\u1ec5n V\u0103n Ho\u00e0ng cho c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u1eaft ch\u00ednh. Tuy nhi\u00ean anh kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh kh\u00f4ng bao gi\u1edd coi c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 trong cu\u1ed9c c\u1ea1nh tranh n\u00e0y.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\" \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n qu\u1ed1c gia, kh\u00f4ng ai trong \u0111\u1ed9i l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a nhau. L\u00e0 c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i s\u1ebd c\u00f9ng nhau t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t. Ai \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh, b\u1eaft ch\u00ednh s\u1ebd ch\u1edd \u0111\u1ee3i quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u1ee7a HLV tr\u01b0\u1edfng. C\u00f9ng v\u1edbi t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 anh em, L\u00e2m s\u1ebd ch\u01a1i h\u1ebft m\u00ecnh, ch\u01a1i m\u00e1u l\u1eeda v\u00ec m\u00e0u c\u1edd s\u1eafc \u00e1o\", th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n \u0110\u1eb7ng V\u0103n L\u00e2m chia s\u1ebb sau bu\u1ed5i t\u1eadp c\u1ee7a Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam chi\u1ec1u 24/7.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ng\u00f4i sao \u0111ang kho\u00e1c \u00e1o CLB H\u1ea3i Ph\u00f2ng c\u0169ng th\u1eadn tr\u1ecdng khi n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 su\u1ea5t b\u1eaft ch\u00ednh tr\u00ean tuy\u1ec3n khi l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u00f3 l\u1ee3i th\u1ebf r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn v\u1ec1 phong \u0111\u1ed9 c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 kinh nghi\u1ec7m thi \u0111\u1ea5u so v\u1edbi 2 th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u0103n L\u00e2m cho bi\u1ebft: \" Kh\u00f4ng v\u00ec h\u01a1n tu\u1ed5i, kinh nghi\u1ec7m m\u00e0 m\u00ecnh t\u1ef1 tin. T\u00f4i ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0m nh\u1eefng g\u00ec t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t c\u00f3 th\u1ec3, gi\u1eef phong \u0111\u1ed9 t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ebfn khi gi\u1ea3i b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u. Vi\u1ec7c c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i l\u00e0 t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n h\u1ebft m\u00ecnh trong c\u00e1c bu\u1ed5i t\u1eadp, l\u00e0 t\u1eadp trung. Nh\u1eefng chuy\u1ec7n kh\u00e1c \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 HLV tr\u01b0\u1edfng gi\u1ea3i quy\u1ebft..<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">L\u00e2m b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd v\u00e0 vinh d\u1ef1 kh\u00ed c\u00f3 t\u00ean trong danh s\u00e1ch l\u1ea7n n\u00e0y. H\u1ed3i \u0111\u1ea7u n\u0103m L\u00e2m v\u00e0 m\u1ecdi ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u1ed5 v\u0169 U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u1edf gi\u1ea3i ch\u00e2u \u00c1, h\u00f4m nay th\u00ec L\u00e2m \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t \u1edf \u0111\u00e2y t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n c\u00f9ng c\u00e1c em chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb thi \u0111\u1ea5u\u201d.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh sinh n\u0103m 1993 c\u0169ng ch\u1ec9 ra s\u1ef1 kh\u00e1c bi\u1ec7t trong c\u00e1ch t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n v\u00e0 thi \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u1eefa \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam so v\u1edbi t\u1ea1i CLB H\u1ea3i Ph\u00f2ng n\u01a1i anh \u0111ang thi \u0111\u1ea5u.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u201cCh\u1eb3ng c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i n\u00f3i nhi\u1ec1u, th\u00e0nh t\u00edch gi\u1ea3i ch\u00e2u \u00c1 \u0111\u00e3 n\u00f3i t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 v\u1ec1 U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam. C\u00e1c b\u1ea1n \u1edf \u0111\u00e2y \u0111\u00e1 nh\u1ecf, ng\u1eafn, nhanh, c\u1ea7m b\u00f3ng \u1edf d\u01b0\u1edbi nhi\u1ec1u c\u00f2n \u1edf H\u1ea3i Ph\u00f2ng th\u00ec \u0111\u1ed9i L\u00e2m hay \u0111\u00e1 d\u00e0i nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n, r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00fap L\u00e2m v\u1ec1 th\u1ec3 l\u1ef1c\", th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh Vi\u1ec7t ki\u1ec1u Nga th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn.</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hang-thu-olympic-viet-nam-su-tu-tin-cua-thay-park-168-191683.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/19/hang-thu-olympic-viet-nam-su-tu-tin-cua-thay-park.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hang-thu-olympic-viet-nam-su-tu-tin-cua-thay-park-168-191683.html\">H\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam: S\u1ef1 t\u1ef1 tin c\u1ee7a th\u1ea7y Park</span><br />\r\n12 \u2013 \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 s\u1ed1 l\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tri\u1ec7u t\u1eadp l\u00ean tuy\u1ec3n Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u1ec3 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb cho chi\u1ebfn d\u1ecbch ASIAD s\u1eafp t\u1edbi. V\u00e0 ta c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 th\u1ea5y \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 t\u1ef1 tin c\u1ee7a HLV Park...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)<o:p></o:p></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1591","checkdouble":"191943"},{"date":"23:50 24/07","title":"Mourinho kh\u00f4ng h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1edbi c\u00f4ng t\u00e1c chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng M.U","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/24/mourinho-muon-mu-co-them-2-tan-binh.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>\u0110\u1ebfn l\u00fac n\u00e0y, c\u00f4ng t\u00e1c chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng M.U ch\u01b0a nh\u01b0 mong mu\u1ed1n c\u1ee7a HLV Jose Mourinho. \u00d4ng mu\u1ed1n Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf c\u00f3 th\u00eam \u00edt nh\u1ea5t 2 t\u00e2n binh ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng n\u1eefa.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>M.U chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng ch\u01b0a t\u1ed1t</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nMan United \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 3 t\u00e2n binh tr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u1ec1m m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi 2018/19. Tuy nhi\u00ean, trong \u0111\u00f3 th\u1ef1c ch\u1ea5t ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 Fred l\u00e0 b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng l\u1edbn v\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n s\u1ebd c\u00f3 t\u1ea7m \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng t\u1edbi Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf trong th\u1eddi gian t\u1edbi. C\u00f2n h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 c\u00e1nh Diogo Dalot v\u00e0 th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh Lee Grant ho\u1eb7c qu\u00e1 non n\u1edbt ho\u1eb7c qu\u00e1 l\u1edbn tu\u1ed5i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nHi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i, M.U \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho l\u00e0 \u0111ang c\u00f3 li\u00ean h\u1ec7 v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng Harry Maguire, Miralem Pjanic v\u00e0 Ivan Perisic. Trung v\u1ec7, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 trung t\u00e2m c\u1ed9ng th\u00eam t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng c\u00e1nh l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng g\u00ec HLV Jose Mourinho y\u00eau c\u1ea7u b\u1ed9 ph\u1eadn chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng M.U b\u1ed5 sung cho m\u00ecnh.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Mourinho mu\u1ed1n chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng MU c\u00f3 th\u00eam 2 t\u00e2n binh h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Mourinho mu\u1ed1n chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng MU c\u00f3 th\u00eam 2 t\u00e2n binh h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/21/Mourinho-muon-chuyen-nhuong-MU-co-them-2-tan-binh-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">M.U m\u1edbi c\u00f3 ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Fred l\u00e0 \u0111\u00e1ng ch\u00fa \u00fd</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>Mourinho ra y\u00eau c\u1ea7u</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTrong m\u1ed9t cu\u1ed9c tr\u1ea3 l\u1eddi ph\u1ecfng v\u1ea5n m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, Mourinho kh\u00f4ng ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 c\u1ee5 th\u1ec3 c\u1ea7n nh\u1eefng ai, song g\u1ee3i \u00fd r\u1eb1ng ch\u01b0a ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1edbi c\u00f4ng t\u00e1c chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u1ebfn l\u00fac n\u00e0y.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cT\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t chuy\u1ec7n\u201d, \u00f4ng n\u00f3i v\u1edbi ESPN. \u201cNh\u1eefng g\u00ec \u0111\u00e3 x\u1ea3y ra ch\u01b0a h\u1eb3n \u0111\u00e3 nh\u01b0 v\u1eady. V\u00e0 l\u00fac n\u00e0y, t\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 th\u00eam 2 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 m\u1edbi n\u1eefa.\u201d<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Mourinho\" title=\"HLV Mourinho\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/24/HLV-Mourinho.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>HLV Mourinho ra y\u00eau c\u1ea7u v\u1ec1 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng M.U</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nChi\u1ec1u s\u00e2u \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh c\u1ee7a M.U s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ki\u1ec3m ch\u1ee9ng sau ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u1ee7a h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 Antonio Valencia. S\u1eafp t\u1edbi, h\u1ecd s\u1ebd l\u1ea7n l\u01b0\u1ee3t g\u1eb7p AC Milan, Liverpool v\u00e0 Real Madrid t\u1ea1i gi\u1ea3i giao h\u1eefu International Champions Cup tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t M\u1ef9.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTr\u01b0\u1edbc Valencia, t\u00e0i n\u0103ng tr\u1ebb Dalot c\u0169ng ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng ngh\u1ec9 t\u1edbi th\u00e1ng 9 c\u00f2n Matteo Darmian nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng s\u1ebd tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i Serie A. \u201cT\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng ngh\u0129 Valencia s\u1ebd k\u1ecbp g\u00f3p m\u1eb7t \u1edf 3 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1edbi\u201d, Mourinho n\u00f3i th\u00eam. \u201c\u0110\u00e2y kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i l\u00fac ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn nh\u1eefng r\u1ee7i ro.\u201d<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cValencia kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u1eadu b\u00e9 n\u1eefa. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i ph\u1ea3i c\u1ea9n tr\u1ecdng v\u1edbi c\u1eadu \u1ea5y v\u00e0 gi\u00fap c\u1eadu \u1ea5y s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng cho m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 mua v\u1ec1 m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi. Dalot m\u1edbi 19 tu\u1ed5i song l\u00e0 h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 ph\u1ea3i t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t \u1edf \u0111\u1ed9 tu\u1ed5i c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. Nh\u01b0ng c\u1eadu \u1ea5y m\u1edbi ph\u1ea3i ph\u1eabu thu\u1eadt v\u00e0 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u00e0ng ph\u1ea3i c\u1ea9n th\u1eadn v\u1edbi Valencia.\u201d<br>\r\n<strong><br>\r\nXem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft v\u1ec1 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng M.U tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/tin-chuyen-nhuong/3-thuong-vu-co-the-se-no-tai-man-united-trong-nhung-ngay-toi-187-191935.html\">3 th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 s\u1ebd n\u1ed5 t\u1ea1i Man United trong nh\u1eefng ng\u00e0y t\u1edbi</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/mu-nhan-tin-buon-tu-muc-tieu-so-1-172-191932.html\">M.U nh\u1eadn tin bu\u1ed3n t\u1eeb m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau s\u1ed1 1</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-italia/hlv-gattuso-muon-bonucci-o-lai-milan-176-191897.html\">HLV Milan n\u00f3i g\u00ec khi Bonucci c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 sang M.U ho\u1eb7c Real?</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/mourinho-noi-gi-ve-viec-mu-chi-50-trieu-bang-mua-alderweireld-172-191725.html\">Mourinho n\u00f3i g\u00ec v\u1ec1 vi\u1ec7c MU chi 50 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng mua Alderweireld?</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nGia Vi (TTVN)</strong><br>\r\n\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1590","checkdouble":"191944"}]}